fulltitle: In Studio from Simply Timeless - Vincent Herring Interview - January 23, 2020
description:
http://www.simplytimelessradio.com

Our In Studio guest this week is the renowned saxophonist Vincent Herring. Recently, Jay Daniels sat down with Vincent to discuss his latest album, "Bird at 100," recorded alongside Bobby Watson and Gary Bartz. Vincent also shares some of his thoughts on the legacy left by Charlie "Bird" Parker. More information on the music of Vincent Herring is available at http://www.vincentherring.com.
